abstract: The computer company and its founder, Michael S. Dell, are accused of financial irregularities stemming from dealings with the chip maker.
snippet: The computer company and its founder, Michael S. Dell, are accused of financial irregularities stemming from dealings with the chip maker.
lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO  Dell said on Thursday that it was in talks with the Securities and Exchange Commission to resolve allegations that it and its founder and chief executive, Michael S. Dell, engaged in financial irregularities related to the company’s dealings with Intel.

headline.main: Dell in Talks to Settle Intel Claims With S.E.C.
headline.print_headline: Dell in Talks To Settle Intel Claims With S.E.C.
